{"tid":1876383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"將0.6元進價口罩賣1元 湖北洪湖一藥房被罰：涉嫌哄抬價格","createTime":"2020-02-12T11:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T13:27:52.000Z","uid":256908,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ba24962aea2fcc3bd7fedc3239ef78f25b950900","tid":1876383,"uid":256908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"【將0.6元進價口罩賣1元 湖北洪湖一藥房被罰：涉嫌哄抬價格】 據湖北洪湖市委宣傳部&ldquo;今日洪湖&rdquo;消息，2月5日，洪湖市市場監督管理局對洪湖市華康大藥房涉嫌哄抬口罩價格行為立案調查。經查，洪湖市華康大藥房銷售一次性口罩38000個，購進價格0.6元/只，銷售價格1元/只，其購銷差價額高過《省市場監管局關於新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎防控期間有關價格違法行為認定與處理的指導意見》文件規定的15%標準，涉嫌哄抬價格。目前，洪湖市市場監督管理局已對該案調查終結，沒收違法所得14210元，罰款人民幣42630元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xr3c4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xr3c4W.jpg&h=6ca00d34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fde031ae28c5930f971d89b537ec9d7a767c7e6","tid":1876383,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"贏粒糖輸間廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b42af4cc28d7c347c1dfb403d45e1dd9c4c59eb","tid":1876383,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"買進價格，銷售價格？ 點解我唔明既...<br />\n抑或係而家行翻共產"},{"pid":"65c88d320f7469658153551f94ba577f9c067a9e","tid":1876383,"uid":68111,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵多過15%利潤俾人拉"},{"pid":"660bdfeaab1bdd9d01999efc27cfa512c610f918","tid":1876383,"uid":45505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"幾時送班藥房佬中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72aaaa0c26d8fd995910cbd9136a280fedb7549","tid":18763